---
title: Monorepo structure (pnpm workspaces)
---
flowchart LR
    classDef app fill:#EDF1F7,stroke:#6D28D9,color:#1A1D24
    classDef pkg fill:#E8ECF2,stroke:#16A34A,color:#1A1D24
    classDef infra fill:#FFF3E0,stroke:#D97706,color:#1A1D24
    classDef docs fill:#F4ECD8,stroke:#5B4636,color:#1A1D24

    Root[(monorepo<br/>pnpm-workspace)]

    Root --> Apps[apps/]
    Root --> Pkgs[packages/]
    Root --> Infra[infra/]
    Root --> Docs[docs/<br/>schema/<br/>diagrams/]:::docs

    Apps --> Mobile[apps/mobile<br/>React Native + Expo]:::app
    Apps --> Web[apps/admin-web<br/>Next.js 14]:::app
    Apps --> API[apps/api<br/>Fastify + Prisma]:::app

    Pkgs --> UI[packages/ui<br/>Neumorphic primitives]:::pkg
    Pkgs --> Types[packages/types<br/>Zod-derived shared types]:::pkg
    Pkgs --> Cfg[packages/config<br/>tsconfig / eslint / prettier]:::pkg

    Infra --> Compose[infra/docker-compose.yml<br/>Postgres + Redis + Minio + ClamAV]:::infra
    Infra --> Actions[infra/github-actions/<br/>CI workflows]:::infra

    Mobile -.->|imports| UI
    Mobile -.->|imports| Types
    Mobile -.->|extends| Cfg
    Web -.->|imports| Types
    Web -.->|extends| Cfg
    API -.->|imports| Types
    API -.->|extends| Cfg
